{"tid":1195141,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怪得利物浦vvd咁勁，比人查到佢係華人血統","createTime":"2019-06-09T14:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:20:09.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"1c57c434d9a3589647d7fd394a0b1d0b939bbd59","tid":1195141,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"據華裔球員信息專家Jallo_Tang爆料，利物浦後衛範戴克擁有華人血統，應為第五代華裔。<br />\n<br />\n Jallo_Tang寫道：<br />\n<br />\n 如果說是父親是帶領範戴克推開足球大門的人， 那麼幫助他走向世界巔峰的則是他的母親。 這個一手獨立將兒子撫養成人的偉大母親，Hellen Fo Sieeuw（海倫-火秀），來自於一個蘇里南華人家庭。<br />\n<br />\n 1872年，客家人陳火秀（Chin Fo Sieeuw，或Chin Fie Kong，音似陳輝江）生於中國廣東，1918年作為勞工前往蘇里南謀生，在蘇里南留下了8個孩子。 最早於1936年，陳火秀決定帶著兩個兒子Paul和Hugo一同回中國，但臨行前由於Hugo生病，陳火秀決心放棄帶走這個兒子，最終拋下其他子女，與兒子Paul踏上了返回中國的 船隻。<br />\n<br />\n 陳家人至此再未見到過陳火秀，而陳火秀的後人，也就是范戴克的表親，目前可能定居在廣東某處（莞深惠可能性極大）。<br />\n<br />\n 說回範戴克，雖然三兄妹裡只有他自己用了父姓，弟弟妹妹皆姓Fo Sieeuw，但是孰輕孰重，他心裡自有分辨，就如同他球衣展示的那樣，他叫Virgil。<br />\n<br />\n Jallo_Tang還在回複評論時表示，範戴克是陳火秀的玄外孫，應該是第五代華裔。"},{"pid":"a4f9d5e1061f00af069cf1164e5fbe0c491a2152","tid":1195141,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"有無證據？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e96fe3406d987878f74fd2441b762d15fcd09d9","tid":1195141,"uid":31151,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 佢個樣都唔似非洲/歐洲人"},{"pid":"56d92493077fb183e0f8aec52bd9e2dc0cbfa980","tid":1195141,"uid":173952,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"a4f9d5e1061f00af069cf1164e5fbe0c491a2152","tid":1195141,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:17:51.000Z","msg":"有無證據？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"佢有個中文名叫范迪克"},{"pid":"6067718aadc6b8cc4b10a2b31bd578c6e16c0fad","tid":1195141,"uid":215715,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但是孰輕孰重，他心裡自有分辨，就如同他球衣展示的那樣，他叫Virgil</span><br />\n荷蘭人就荷蘭人啦<br />\n係咪要搞到全世界華人都被人當養唔熟既狗呀<br />\n1872年你出生廣東都係南蠻黎炸傻仔<br />\n真係當你一家人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf532eb8db48d2584e2a2b2a669d783c3d5eeda1","tid":1195141,"uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"回家代表中國隊吧"},{"pid":"6e458e003a965e694b5617e26786eaedcd1954de","tid":1195141,"uid":26959,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"張曦雯係佢個孖生阿妹"},{"pid":"264a73533d209403263c5d352df784becde207c5","tid":1195141,"uid":94739,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"利物浦大把華人球員啦<br />\n<br />\n張伯倫，高美斯，文尼，馬貼<br />\n<br />\n全部中國人姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840b5e73e4aa6f3d1ee1170ef34b77cee72fa3e2","tid":1195141,"uid":158145,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"264a73533d209403263c5d352df784becde207c5","tid":1195141,"uid":94739,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"利物浦大把華人球員啦<br />\n<br />\n張伯倫，高美斯，文尼，馬貼<br />\n<br />\n全部中國人姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯，古天奴，史達寧"},{"pid":"7f14e8b69e15bb0d38785c52ddb39ba7015ade9e","tid":1195141,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"快d認祖歸宗啦"},{"pid":"069a9f858de28d84a148f91d66e752dd9328904b","tid":1195141,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56d92493077fb183e0f8aec52bd9e2dc0cbfa980","tid":1195141,"uid":173952,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"quote":{"pid":"a4f9d5e1061f00af069cf1164e5fbe0c491a2152","tid":1195141,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci